<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/39875075" target="_blank" data-id="8157375" data-za-element-name="Title">
如何快速开发多端应用?
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/39875075/answer/84598715">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="29270763">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="84598715"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
<a class="zm-item-vote-count js-expand js-vote-count" href="javascript:;" data-bind-votecount>155</a>
</div>

