<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/27664804" target="_blank" data-id="3248808" data-za-element-name="Title">
学了多种编程语言的不乱套吗？
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/27664804/answer/38103283">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="10632721">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="38103283"> -->

