<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/36882354" target="_blank" data-id="6960074" data-za-element-name="Title">
非计算机专业，现在在学习javascript，想学习数据结构和算法如何入门?
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/36882354/answer/69416260">
<!-- <meta itemprop="answer-id" content="23186318">
<meta itemprop="answer-url-token" content="69416260"> -->

<div class="zm-item-vote">
