<h2><a class="question_link" href="/question/39729094" target="_blank" data-id="8099164" data-za-element-name="Title">
为什么看到有的前端工程师将css每个选择器里的内容写成一行?
</a></h2>
<div class="expandable entry-body">
<link itemprop="url" href="/question/39729094/answer/82891814">
