<div class="zm-item-rich-text expandable js-collapse-body" data-resourceid="1284440" data-action="/answer/content" data-author-name="学习网站收集控" data-entry-url="/question/22759296/answer/31737189">

<textarea hidden class="content">html视频教程&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//yangqingfeng.com/33.html&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;盗雪html5入门基础视频教程下载汇总&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;css视频教程&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//yangqingfeng.com/31.html&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;盗雪css视频教程_2013年&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;javascript视频教程 &lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.zhinengshe.com/video.html&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;JavaScript视频教程&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;另外，学习网站你得找我，来个劲爆的，&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//1nami.com/&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;学习网站导航&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt; 一个专门收集高质量国内外学习网站的小众站点。上面公开课、web开发、移动开发、医疗、科研、外语、国外mooc等各类学习网站都有所收集。&lt;b&gt;列下清单~&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;br&gt;一、汇总榜单：&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//1nami.com/site/167.html&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;公开课_学习网站导航&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//1nami.com/site/167.html&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;收录了网易、多贝、传课等众多公开课学习网站&lt;i class=&quot;icon-external&quot;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//1nami.com/site/169.html&quot; class=&quot; wrap external&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;n